_sText:
Synopsis

"Why does it always happen? It is sunny in here.. but I feel blue, I can't go to war anymore." - SGT. Red

Key goals:

Terrorists: Blow up either one of the bomb sites
Counter-Terrorists: Neutralize and prevent the terrorists from blowing up the sites

Information:

5v5 defusal map set on a rural area somewhere in the province of laguna, philippines.
This is my first ever map that aims to be competitive/balanced when it comes to team/gameplay.
It takes two years to finalize the layout, and half a year to resemble the theme.
It's quite a long run, but this map is by far the most exhausting map I've ever done.

Other notes:

Bot quota is limited only to 5, same goes to player spawns.
This is an early look for the possible design of the map, the version is in beta.
If you encounter any bugs, let me know in the comments.
